{
  "stem": "10829.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I went through this one time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was at the Jewish Center.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had the dispatch came for an interview, and it was me and Alfred Tibor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You heard of him?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went through about 2 hours, 2 and 1/2 hours of this whole thing-- interviews and all this-- had on TV.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You blinked your eyes, and we were gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] Oh, I was furious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Less than that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Might as well get comfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This all right, or?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in 1935, to the best of my knowledge, [INAUDIBLE] from where in Europe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as the dates are concerned, my mother tells me somewhere around that time, but to the best of my knowledge, it was 1935 in October.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in a city called Trochenbrod.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's actually, it's Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's up near Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The countries have changed so many times during my lifetime that we figure it is basically [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a small little town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Jewish, they called it Trochenbrod.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Basically, it's because our city was full of [YIDDISH], [YIDDISH] meaning mud.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's where you got it in as trochen, the town, and [YIDDISH], meaning mud.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have any-- any paved streets or anything, but it was a big, long street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in Polish or Ukrainian they called it Zofjowka, and it laid near our-- our-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] capital, or wherever we went to-- to register at a hospital was either Lutsk, [NON-ENGLISH], or Rowne.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Rowne, which was about, to the best of my figurings, around 350 to 400 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Lutsk, we used to-- that was the big city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's where your hospitals, your records were kept.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
